msgid "Tech That"
msgstr "Teknoolajiga"

msgid "Matters"
msgstr "Muhiimsan"

msgid "Innoso is a collective of passionate young developers creating world-class software for businesses, governments, and individuals — built with craftsmanship, delivered with care."
msgstr "Innoso waa koox hoggaaminaysa oo hodan ah oo dhallinyarada ah ee abuuraya barnaamijyo heer-caalami ah ganacsiyada, dowladaha, iyo shakhsiyaadka — dhisaysa si tayo leh, si xanaanada leh loogu soo gaarsiiyaa."

msgid "See Our Work"
msgstr "Arag Shaqadayada"

msgid "Always on time"
msgstr "Had iyo jeer wakhtiga"

msgid "Available now"
msgstr "Hadda waa la heli karaa"

msgid "Projects Delivered"
msgstr "Mashaariic La Dhammaystiray"

msgid "Happy Clients"
msgstr "Macaamiil Faraxsan"

msgid "Countries Served"
msgstr "Wadamo La Adeegay"

msgid "Satisfaction"
msgstr "Raalli-gelinta"

msgid "Who We Are"
msgstr "Yaan Nahay"

msgid "Built Different."
msgstr "Si kala duwan loo dhisay."

msgid "By Design."
msgstr "Si loo Naqshadeeyey."

msgid "A group of talented young developers united by one mission: making technology accessible, impactful, and beautiful."
msgstr "Koox xirfadlayaasha dhallinyarada ah oo mideysan hal hawlood: si loo sameeyo teknoolajiga mid la gaari karo, saameyn leh, oo qurux badan."

msgid "Our Mission"
msgstr "Hawsheenna"

msgid "To empower businesses, governments, and individuals by delivering high-quality, modern software that solves real problems — built with craftsmanship, delivered with care."
msgstr "Si loo xoogaysiiyo ganacsiyada, dowladaha, iyo shakhsiyaadka iyaga oo siinaya barnaamijyo casri ah oo tayo sare leh ee xalliya dhibaatooyinka dhabta ah — dhisaysa si tayo leh, si xanaanada leh loogu soo gaarsiiyaa."

msgid "Our Vision"
msgstr "Aragtidayada"

msgid "To become the most trusted tech partner in our region — where clients choose us not just for our code, but for our commitment to their success and our ability to grow with them."
msgstr "In aanu noqono xulafada teknoolajiga ee ugu la-aaminsan degaankayaga — halkaas oo macaamiilku naga doortaan, ma aha oo keliya koodhkayaga, balse waajibkooda guushooda iyo kartideenna in aannu la korino."

msgid "What We Build"
msgstr "Waxa aan Dhisno"

msgid "Every Layer of Your"
msgstr "Dhammaan Lakabada"

msgid "Digital Stack"
msgstr "Dijital-kaaga"

msgid "From idea to launch — we cover every layer of your digital needs with precision and care."
msgstr "Fikradda ilaa la-dhaafinta — waxaan daboolnaa dhammaan lakabada baahiyahaaga dijital-ka si saxsan iyo xanaanada leh."

msgid "Custom Web Apps"
msgstr "Apps Internetka Gaar ah"

msgid "Tailor-made web solutions built for your unique challenges, designed to scale with your growth."
msgstr "Xalal Internet ah oo gaar loogu sameeyey caqabadahaaga gaarka ah, loo naqshadeeyay inay la koraan kobocaaga."

msgid "Mobile Apps"
msgstr "Apps Moobilka"

msgid "Native and cross-platform apps delivering seamless, polished experiences on iOS and Android."
msgstr "Apps asalka ah iyo kuwa tartiib badan oo keena waayo-aragnimo siin-daran oo sifaysan iOS iyo Android."

msgid "Enterprise Systems"
msgstr "Nidaamyada Ganacsiga"

msgid "Robust, secure platforms for enterprises and public-sector organizations demanding reliability."
msgstr "Madal xooggan oo ammaan ah oo loogu talagalay ganacsiyada iyo ururrada qaybta dadweynaha ee baahisan xasilloonida."

msgid "E-commerce"
msgstr "Ganacsiga Elektarooniga"

msgid "Complete online stores with payments, inventory management, and powerful analytics."
msgstr "Dukaammada khadka ah ee dhamaystiran oo leh lacag-bixinno, maamulka kaydka, iyo falanqayn xooggan."

msgid "Landing Pages"
msgstr "Bogagga Soo-dejinta"

msgid "High-converting, beautifully designed pages that attract customers and represent your brand."
msgstr "Bogago si fiican loo naqshadeeyay oo soo-jiidanaya macaamiilka oo u muujinaya calaamadaada ganacsiga."

msgid "Dashboards"
msgstr "Sabuuradaha"

msgid "Intuitive control centers delivering real-time insight and full control over your operations."
msgstr "Xarumaha xukumaadka ee dahsoon oo bixiya faahfaahin xilli-ku-meel ah iyo xukun buuxa hawlgalkaaga."

msgid "Tech Consulting"
msgstr "La-talinta Teknoolajiga"

msgid "Strategic guidance to help your business overcome challenges and unlock growth through technology."
msgstr "Hagi xeelad ah si loo gaargaaro ganacsigaaga inuu ka gudbo caqabadaha ugana furo kobaca teknoolajiga."

msgid "How We Work"
msgstr "Sidaan u Shaqeyno"

msgid "Simple."
msgstr "Fudud."

msgid "Transparent."
msgstr "Hufan."

msgid "Fast."
msgstr "Dhakhso."

msgid "A proven three-step process to get you from idea to a live product — efficiently and reliably."
msgstr "Hannaan laba-iyo-labaatan-jeerkii ah oo saddex-tallaabood ah si laguu geliyo fikradda ilaa alaabta tooska ah — si wax-ku-ool ah iyo la-aaminsan."

msgid "Discover"
msgstr "Baadhin"

msgid "We listen deeply to understand your vision, goals, and constraints before writing a single line of code."
msgstr "Waxaan si qoto dheer u dhagaysan inaan fahanno aragtidaada, ambacyadaada, iyo xaddidaadaha ka hor inta aanaan qorin hal xariiq oo koodh ah."

msgid "Design & Build"
msgstr "Naqshadeyn & Dhismid"

msgid "Our team designs and develops your solution with modern technology and continuous feedback loops."
msgstr "Kooxdayadu waxay naqshadeysaa oo horumarisaa xalkaaga teknoolajiga casriga ah iyo wareegga jawaab-celinta joogtada ah."

msgid "Launch & Support"
msgstr "Furitaan & Taageero"

msgid "We deploy, test, and hand over a polished product — then stay available for ongoing support."
msgstr "Waxaan geyno, tijaabiyo, oo u dhiibno alaab la safeeyay — ka dibna waxaan joognaa taageerada joogtada ah."

msgid "Portfolio"
msgstr "Portfoliyaha"

msgid "Real Solutions,"
msgstr "Xalal Dhab ah,"

msgid "Real Impact"
msgstr "Saamayn Dhab ah"

msgid "Explore some of the products we've built for clients across industries and borders."
msgstr "Sahamin qaar ka mid ah alaabta aannu u dhisay macaamiilka warshadaha iyo xuduudaha kala duwan."

msgid "Projects coming soon"
msgstr "Mashaariicda way soo socotaan"

msgid "Check back shortly — we're updating our portfolio."
msgstr "Soo noqo dhawaan — waxaan cusbooneysiinayaa Portfoliyahayaga."

